Ibitaro bya CARAES Ndera, byatangiye kubakwa mu mwaka w' 1968 , bikaba ar'ibitaro bifasha abarwayi bafite uburwayi bwo mu mutwe.

== Amateka ==
<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/kwibuka/article/abarwayi-bo-mu-mutwe-muri-caraes-ndera-ngo-bishwe-n-aba-para-commando-b-i-kanombe</ref>Ibitaro bya CARAES i Ndera n’ibitaro byashinzwe mu mwaka w’1968 n'abavandimwe b'abagiraneza, itorero mpuzamahanga ry’amadini ya pontifique, nyuma y'icyifuzo cya guverinoma y'u [[Rwanda]] na Kiliziya Gatolika yaho yo kurekura abarwayi bo mu mutwe bava mu magereza y'igihugu.

Abarwayi ba mbere bakiriwe mu bitaro mu 1972. Uburyo bwakoreshejwe kwari ugutezimbere serivisi zita ku buzima bwo mu mutwe zishingiye ku mibereho n’umuco mu [[Rwanda]].

Mumwaka w' 1994 Muribibitaro haguye inzirakarengane nyishi zazize [[Itsembabwoko ry’u Rwanda ry’1994|genocide yakorewe abatutsi]] Umuyobozi Mukuru w’ibitaro bya Caraes Ndera, Frère Charles Nkubili avuga ko mu 1994 ku itariki 17 Mata<ref>https://rwanda.shafaqna.com/FR/AL/219259</ref>, ari bwo abasirikare n’interahamwe bagabye ibitero bakica abantu bose batagiriye imbabazi abarwayi bo mu mutwe<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/kwibuka/article/abarwayi-bo-mu-mutwe-muri-caraes-ndera-ngo-bishwe-n-aba-para-commando-b-i-kanombe</ref>.

== Aho biherereye ==
Ibi bitaro biherereye mu [[Akarere ka Gasabo]], umurenge wa Ndera.

== Uko bikora ==
Abatanga ubuvuzi bwo mu mutwe bafite uruhare runini cyane mu gukumira, gusuzuma, kuvura no gusubiza mu buzima busanzwe abarwayi bo muri CARAES Ndera n'amashami yacyo ya CARAES [[Butare]] Psychiatric Centre na Icyizere Psychotherapeutic Centre.<ref>https://hi-in.facebook.com/igihe/posts/10159232740167114</ref>

* Kwita ku barwayi bo mu mutwe n'indwara zo mu mutwe zoherejwe n'ibindi bigo nderabuzima. 
* Kwemeza ubugenzuzi bwa tekiniki mubuzima bwo mumutwe mubitaro byakarere kubufatanye bwa minisiteri yubuzima.                                                                      
* Guhugura inzobere mu buzima mu buzima bwo mu mutwe
* Kwigisha abanyeshuri b'imbere ninzobere mubuzima kubijyanye n'ubuzima bwo mumutwe.

== Ubutumwa bw'ibitaro ==
Gutanga ubuvuzi bwiza bufite ubuhanga n’ubwitange ku barwayi bo mu mutwe n’ubuvuzi bw’imitsi baturuka mu gihugu hose, no Kwiyemeza kwigisha abahanga mu buzima bwo mu mutwe<ref>https://caraesnderahospital.rw/mission.php#</ref>.

== Icyerekezo cy'ibitaro ==
Gutanga ubuvuzi bwiza bwuzuye kubarwayi bose boherejwe; guhinduka inyigisho n'ibitaro byohererezwa abarwayi bo mu karere ka Afurika yo Hagati n'Uburasirazuba.

